window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Marrying a demon and fighting a psychotic god, all part of a day’s work.</b></p> <p>Annowan might have finally joined my family, but our marriage doesn’t mean we can afford to slack off!</p> <p>My wives and I are on the trail of another of the Bitch Goddess’s missing generals. Our quest brings us to a desolate, cursed region, where we’ll have to contend with clockwork horrors, undead hordes, and my demonic grandmother-in-law.</p> <p>Things might look rough, but I swore to rescue my sweetheart from the Bitch’s clutches, and nothing will get in my way!</p> <p><i>This book is intended for mature listeners due to descriptions of violence and unconventional relationships. </i></p>"; 
